Actually, the first one over was duped by Disney.  The whole "over the 
cliff" thing was staged by the Disney camera crew filming a documentary 
called "White Wilderness".  Lemmings were tossed onto a snow-covered 
turntable and tossed off a cliff to simulate the mad exodus over the edge:

http://www.snopes.com/disney/films/lemmings.htm
http://www.jimloy.com/biology/lemmings.htm
http://www.wildlifenews.alaska.gov/index.cfm?adfg=wildlife_news.view_article&issue_id=6&articles_id=56

